## Data Privacy Notice

This system processes personal financial information. In a production environment, ensure compliance with:
- General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)
- California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA)
- Financial data protection regulations in your jurisdiction
- Industry standards (PCI DSS if handling payment data)

Users must be informed about:
- What data is collected
- How it's used
- How it's stored and protected
- Their rights to access, modify, and delete their data

